<A>__{darwin wanders the cobbled streets of malvern, pausing occasionally to consult a hand written address. it is starting to rain as, finally, he arrives at the address he is looking for. a substantial terraced house. darwin descends a stone staircase to the imposing front door, and rings the bell. as he waits for an answer a woman appears, unseen in the rain streaked window above, observing him. darwin rings again. a moment later the woman answers the door.}
